    {
      "segment_id": "10",
      "text": "Okay. So, this call is related to your travel light plan, okay? So we have received your proposal. To process your proposal, we will be conducting this call, okay? During the call, I'll ask you a few questions to verify your medical history and your answers will be the part of your insurance application. Okay?",
