      "start_timestamp": "00:37",
      "end_timestamp": "00:44"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "12",
      "text": "In case, in future, if we get to know any information shared by you is incorrect or is wrong, so there is a possibility of a cancellation of your policy or your claim may get rejected.",
